data.description: No Showings until OPEN HOUSE this Sunday, October 15th from 2 - 4!!! This secluded beauty sits on 2.44 acres with a private driveway and a concrete pad in the front for additional parking. 4 sided brick with a rocking chair front porch, 2 car garage, and fenced back yard. Foyer opens up to the family room with tall ceilings, built in shelving and cabinets, and a wood burning fireplace. Do you enjoy cooking? This kitchen is a chef's paradise with the solid surface countertops, 6 burner gas stove with pot filler faucet, stainless steel appliances, shelving, spice racks. Not only is there a nice big sink that overlooks the backyard, but also has an additional sink next to the stove, perfect for washing and preparing those veggies. Separate coffee station with cabinets for storage, walk in pantry with lots of shelving, nice sized laundry room off of the kitchen. Whether your preparing for your meals for the family or entertaining guests, this open concept kitchen/dining room makes a great area to gather. Large owner's suite with trey ceilings, separate garden tub and shower, double sinks, his and hers closets. Secondary bedrooms are nicely sized with great closet space. Main bathroom has a shower tub combo, new flooring and paint. The backyard is level and is a little slice of paradise, with the covered back porch, pergola, and small inground pool. Small stainless steel sink for washing your hands after a day of gardening or preparing food to throw on the grill. Shade or sun, this place has it all. A short drive to shopping, eating, and I-75.
